1
00:00:02,040 --> 00:00:05,040
- There's no turning you, is there?
- No.

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:06,760
Then I'll take you as you are.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:08,680
You, my friend, don't know who I am.

4
00:00:08,720 --> 00:00:11,840
Never come back to
Herot. You're dead to me.

5
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:13,760
Play the part your
mother has set for you.

6
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:16,239
She'll not be expecting when
we take power from her.

7
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:18,040
Do you want to be Thane?

8
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,800
Tell my uncle I am done with him.

9
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:25,040
You have hid in the
shadows for too long.

10
00:00:25,080 --> 00:00:26,880
If you want power, take it.

11
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:29,840
If I tell my mother the
truth, I'll lose her trust.

12
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:32,439
And with it, any chance of ever ruling.

13
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:34,720
But if Abrecan
attacks, Herot could fall.

14
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:39,240
I have a vision for
us... to be the greatest tribe.

15
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:44,400
Abrecan is going to attack Herot.

